title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 5 - Oct 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay and Buck’s Countdown to Election Day Episode 5 - Oct 23 2022
description:
Seven sensational candidates – Kari Lake (AZ), Anna Paulina Luna (FL), Karoline Leavitt (NH), Tim Michels (WI), Joe Kent (WA), Mark Ronchetti (NM) and Sen Marco Rubio (FL) – plus, why all candidates should study Kari Lake’s campaign.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
